<h2>Skiing Hotels</h2>
<p><img src="/media/13049728/sport-hotel-hermitage-terrace.jpg" alt="hotelhero" data-udi="umb://media/4626274a19a949e6b8b7453e0e6616c7" /></p>
<p>Skiing holidays are all about making the most of the great outdoors - testing your skills on the slopes, taking in the fresh air and appreciating the amazing scenery. After a full day of skiing though, it is so important to return to your hotel and it feel cosy, relaxing and have everything you need. </p>
<p>Hotels are the perfect accommodation choice if you are looking for great service, a hearty breakfast, skiing convenience and a room with a view.</p>
<p>Inghams offers a wide selection of hotels, ensuring your ideal choice is available. From luxury &amp; spa hotels, family friendly hotels to ski-in ski-out hotels, you will be able to find the right one for you. </p>
<p>Our range of hotel offerings means you can select rooms with a balcony to soak up your surroundings, rooms with space for a family so you can all be together and rooms with 5* facilities and service so you can sit back and relax. </p>
</div>
